  "text": "One of the most important aspects in the electronics equipment is the property of operating without causing interference to neighboring subsystems; there are different considerations that can be applied in the design of the PCB for better performance in electromagnetic compatibility (EMC). One must be sure to minimize the area of the loop, not to place circuits between connectors, control the transition time from digital signals and provide return signal plane [CITATION_1] .",
